{"timestamp": "2025-12-12 16:19:35.263395", "event": "llm_start", "messages": "content='Based on the diagnosis report: **Anomaly**\\n\\n- `host_1_1` (10.0.0.1) cannot reach `host_2_1` (10.0.0.5).  \\n  The ping shows *Destination Host Unreachable* coming from 10.0.0.1.\\n\\n**Faulty device**\\n\\n- The leaf switch that connects the two hosts (`leaf_1`) has no interface on the 10.0.0.0/24 network.  \\n  Its routing table only knows the 20.0.0.0/24 network (via `eth6`).\\n\\n**Root cause**\\n\\n- The leaf switch is mis‑configured (or the link is missing) for the 10.0.0.0/24 subnet that the hosts use.  \\n  Because `leaf_1` has no interface or route to that subnet, packets from `host_1_1` (and any other host on 10.0.0.0/24) cannot be forwarded to `host_2_1`.  \\n\\n**Result**\\n\\n- Hosts on the 10.0.0.0/24 network are isolated from each other; any traffic between them is dropped with “Destination Host Unreachable”., please provide the submission. Do not submit if no report available.' additional_kwargs={} response_metadata={} id='fa79c6f3-4b6d-4868-8729-2411f6d65902'", "model": {"lc": 1, "type": "not_implemented", "id": ["langchain_ollama", "chat_models", "ChatOllama"], "repr": "ChatOllama(model='gpt-oss:20b', validate_model_on_init=True, temperature=0.0, base_url='http://10.68.186.140:11434')", "name": "ChatOllama"}}
